tags.description: The Community Center includes a fitness room, outdoor pool, multipurpose rooms, cafe area, deck, etc. Also includes Tom Kelly Grand Lawn and Demonstration Gardens. The recreation area is managed (for Cordera use only) by YMCA of the Pikes Peak Region.
